name: Gate Entry Register DFM
query:
select
    ge.name as "Gate Entry NO.",
    ge.date as "Entry Date:Date",
    ge.gate_entry_type as "Gate Entry Type",
    ge.supplier as "Party Name",
    ge.party_contact_person as "Person Name",
    ge.vehicle_no as "Vehical No.",
    ge.in_time as "Incoming Time",
    ge.supplier_invoice_date as "Supplier Invoice Date:Date",
    ge.supplier_bill_no as "Supplier Bill No",
    ge.company as "Company",
    ge.purchase_order as "PO No"
 
from 
    `tabGate Entry`ge  
    
where ge.company=%(company)s and
ge.date >=%(from_date)s and ge.date<=%(to_date)s
order by ge.date  desc ;
